div.p:
Where haſt thou ever read in thy days (ſaid Menn
                     •

               ) in the writings of the Apoſtles, that Chriſt or the Apoſtles ever cryed out to the Magiſtrates for their Power, againſt them that would not hear their Doctrine, nor obey their words, I know certainly ſaid he, that where the Magiſtrate ſhall baniſh with the Sword, there is not the right knowledge of the Spiritual Word, nor Church of Chriſt, it is, Invocare brachium ſeculare.
